  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:0",
      "text": "texturing stage 是我非常享受的阶段，也是我真正能把自己的 art style 加入正在制作的 character、prop 或 vehicle 的阶段。",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:3",
      "text": "How old is the truck?（这辆 truck 有多旧？）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:5",
      "text": "在 texturing 中，我知道表现其 age 的最佳方式，是在 main paint 上加入 wear、stains 和 patina。",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:6",
      "text": "Clean or Dirty?（干净还是脏？）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:8",
      "text": "What was the primary color the van had been repainted in?（这辆 van 重新喷涂后的 primary color 是什么？）",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:10",
      "text": "How can I show a bit of its past life?（如何展示它过去 life 的一点痕迹？）",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:12",
      "text": "What text/decals can I use to amplify the story?（可以用哪些 text/decals 来强化 story？）",
      "ascii_letters": 53,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:14",
      "text": "决定在 Substance Painter 中为 van 制作 texture 后，我能够利用非常有用的 RenderMan Preset Browser，这是 RenderMan 随附的 material 和 lighting preset library。",
      "ascii_letters": 86,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:15",
      "text": "它也是 Substance Painter 中的一个 panel，只需单击一下，就能让我快速、轻松地把 materials 直接从 Painter 导出到符合 RenderMan 的 DCC。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 32
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:16",
      "text": "它会替我完成所有 manual work，确实非常节省时间。它会为 Painter 中任何或所有 selected materials 的所有 channels 导出 .exr files，然后把这些 texture files 转换为 RenderMan 的 .tex format。",
      "ascii_letters": 80,
      "cjk_chars": 39
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:17",
      "text": "获得这些 files 后，它会创建一个 preset，并创建 shading network，全部准备好让我加载到 Solaris（或 Blender、Maya、Katana 等）中。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 27
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:18",
      "text": "VanTurntable_v01.mov",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "4a466ac5be:19",
